The paper discusses explainable recommendation algorithms and their application in recommender systems. This topic falls under the intersection of several sub-fields in computer science, including information retrieval (IR), machine learning (LG), artificial intelligence (AI), human-computer interaction (HC), and social and information networks (SI). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.IR, cs.LG, and cs.AI, followed by cs.HC and cs.SI.
